{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["iOS"],"tokens":[{"text":"optional","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"pushwoosh"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"_","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"pushwoosh","kind":"internalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshiOS\/documentation\/PushwooshFramework\/Pushwoosh","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)Pushwoosh","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"Pushwoosh"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"text":"onMessageReceived","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"message","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"PWMessage","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)PWMessage"},{"kind":"text","text":")"}]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"Overview","text":"Overview","type":"heading","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This method is invoked when a push notification arrives, regardless of app state:"}]},{"items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Foreground"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":": Called immediately when notification arrives","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Background"}]},{"type":"text","text":": Called when system wakes your app to process the notification"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Use this method to:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Log notification receipt for analytics","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Update local data based on notification content"}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Refresh UI if app is in foreground","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Trigger background data sync","type":"text"}]}]}]},{"text":"Foreground Behavior","type":"heading","anchor":"Foreground-Behavior","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"When the app is in foreground, notifications are received but not displayed by default. Use ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshiOS\/documentation\/PushwooshFramework\/Pushwoosh\/showPushnotificationAlert","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" to control this behavior."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"heading","text":"Example","level":2,"anchor":"Example"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Track notification receipt and update local data:","type":"text"}]},{"code":["func pushwoosh(_ pushwoosh: Pushwoosh, onMessageReceived message: PWMessage) {","    Analytics.log(\"push_received\", [","        \"campaign_id\": message.customData?[\"campaign_id\"] ?? \"\",","        \"app_state\": UIApplication.shared.applicationState.rawValue","    ])","","    if let action = message.customData?[\"action\"] as? String {","        switch action {","        case \"refresh_orders\":","            OrderManager.shared.refreshOrders()","        case \"update_cart\":","            CartManager.shared.syncWithServer()","        default:","            break","        }","    }","}"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Show in-app notification banner when app is in foreground:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"code":["func pushwoosh(_ pushwoosh: Pushwoosh, onMessageReceived message: PWMessage) {","    guard UIApplication.shared.applicationState == .active else { return }","","    let banner = InAppNotificationBanner(","        title: message.title ?? \"New Notification\",","        message: message.message ?? \"\"","    )","    banner.show()","}"],"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing"}]}],"seeAls